=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_XLine_ex1 ===

DESCRIPTION: A bright mixed sound, with saw_like oscillator character around 1338 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: bright
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: mixed
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 1337.6851
  harmonic_decay_rate: -0.4106
  harmonic_regularity: 0.8045
  pitch_clarity: 33.0348
  inharmonicity: 0.4882
  type: saw_like
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -2.5164
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: XLine Example 1
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/XLine.html
